<br>
Ok so we prepare. My friend plays a 60dru and 50sk, and his brother switched to his 53 mage. We port to SF and run to the spot that I know so well by now <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
What shall I say, within 20mins of us being there Nezekezena spawned and dropped embers for me! Woot! We decided to stay to get embers for the other mage too. And you wont believe it, five mins later Neze spawned and dropped embers again! This was truly a lucky day for us <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
After this we were about to depart, when Phurzikon spawned...and you perhaps guessed it, he dropped embers too!<br>
<br>
Since they are NO DROP but not LORE I took them and later put them into my bank. This means that if YOU need the embers for a MQ on Quellious, send me a tell!<br>
<br>
Izudin, 59 Conjurer on Quellious (now 4 steps to epic <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
